---
import teamImg from '../assets/images/legal-team.jpeg';
---
<section class="bg-gray-100 py-16 px-6 lg:px-0">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <!-- Left: Text Content -->
      <div class="flex-1 text-center lg:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 leading-tight">
          Your Trusted Legal Partner for Life’s Toughest Moments
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4 max-w-xl">
          With over 20 years of combined experience, our dedicated legal team offers compassionate, strategic, and aggressive representation across family law, business law, criminal defense, and personal injury.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4 max-w-xl">
          We take pride in providing personalized legal solutions tailored to your unique circumstances, ensuring you’re supported every step of the way—from consultation to courtroom.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-xl">
          Whether you’re facing a dispute, launching a business, or seeking justice, we stand by your side to protect your rights and pursue the outcome you deserve.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white text-lg font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded shadow">
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Right: Hero Image -->
      <div class="flex-1">
        <img 
          src={teamImg.src} 
          alt="Professional law team in office" 
          class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full object-cover max-h-[500px]" 
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  